'''Talmo''' is a rural locality in the north eastern part of the [[Riverina]].  It is situated by road, about 12 kilometres south from [[Bookham, New South Wales|Bookham]] and 24 kilometres east from [[Jugiong, New South Wales|Jugiong]].  It has a population within a 7 kilometre radius of approximately 352 people.<ref>[http://www.fallingrain.com/world/AS/2/Talmo.html www.fallingrain.com Talmo]</ref> 


